<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4616929>
    dc:description "Figs 1–5. Habitus of adults, lateral view. 1–2. Caryanda amplexicerca Ou, Liu & Zheng, 2007, ♂, ♀, paratypes. 3–4. C. cyanonota sp. nov., ♂, ♀. 5. C. shuangjianga sp. nov., ♂. Scale bars=5mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4616929/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4616935>
    dc:description "Figs 11–19. Caryanda cyanonota sp. nov. 11–12. Terminalia, ♂, dorsal and lateral views. 13–14. Abdominal apex, ♀, lateral and ventral views. 15–16. Phallic complex, lateral and apical views. 17–19. Epiphallus, dorsal, lateral and posterior views. Scale bars= 1mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4616935/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

